n" dir="ltr">不，但在半个世界之外，在有人阻止我之前我从来没有唱过那首歌，拜托</p><p>— 利亚姆·加拉格尔 (@liamgallagher) <a href="https://twitter.com/liamgallagher/status/1710202655790747967?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 10 月 6 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">不远了</p><p>— 利亚姆·加拉格尔 (@liamgallagher) <a href="https://twitter.com/liamgallagher/status/1711614298273841398?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 10 月 10 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>他补充道：“当然，你得到了一切（‘绝对可能’），一些 Norty b 面甚至可能会推出（Oasis 翻唱<a href="/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>的歌曲）‘I Am The Walrus’，只是为了鳄鱼和胸管。”</p><p>在其他地方，加拉格尔表示，虽然他不会演唱“带我走”，但他将演唱诺埃尔·加拉格尔演唱的歌曲“半个世界”，该歌曲因作为<em>罗伊尔家族</em>的主题曲而闻名。 “在有人阻止我之前我从来没有唱过这首歌，”他在推特上谈到了这首歌。</p><p>在被问及《Live Forever》B 面《Cloudburst》是否会出现在歌单上之后，他还表示，他“昨天正在听（Oasis B 面），这确实让我震惊”。他补充道：“它在名单上，Rkid”</p><p>在谈到他在巡演时最想表演的歌曲时，他说“Married With Children”，并表示他“从未现场表演过”。他还向歌迷保证，独立单曲《Whatever》肯定会“在名单上”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3513295" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3513295" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3513295" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-posing.jpg" alt="白色房间 Noel Gallagher 和 Liam Gallagher 以及 OASIS、Liam Gallagher 和 Noel Gallagher 在英国电视节目拍摄现场的照片（摄影：Des Willie/Redferns）来自 Getty" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3513295" class="wp-caption-text">白色房间 Noel Gallagher 和 Liam Gallagher 以及 OASIS、Liam Gallagher 和 Noel Gallagher 在英国电视节目拍摄现场的照片（摄影：Des Willie/Redferns），来源：Getty</figcaption></figure><p>在 2024 年的“Definitely, Maybe”巡演中，利亚姆将单独录制这张唱片，因为他的兄弟、前乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher</a> ) 一直直言<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-confirms-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-for-2024-denies-oasis-reunion-tour-3436441">不会很快重聚。然而，诺埃尔确实确认了这张开创性专辑的 30 周年纪念重新发行</a>。</p><p> According to the musician, the 30th anniversary reissue of &#39;Definitely Maybe&#39; will include a host of previously lost songs — which were made during the recording sessions at the time. Telling Italian newspaper <em>Corriere Della Sera</em> how the tracks were uncovered, he said: “In the Sony archives we&#39;ve found tapes dating to those sessions.”</p><p> “We thought they were lost, but they were mislabelled,” he added. “They are wonderful versions of those songs, some acoustic versions.”</p><p> He also reaffirmed that fans shouldn&#39;t hope to see any live renditions of the new songs anytime soon. “There won&#39;t be a tour,” he said. “We won&#39;t come back to play them together.” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Noel Gallagher 谈“议会天空”、人工智能绿洲、1975 年和英国脱欧" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qUl5BVqtNZU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> While <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/noel-gallagher-interview-oasis-council-skies-3451058">speaking to <em>NME</em> as part of the latest in our In Conversation series,</a> Noel was asked if Oasis had ever been made any offers for a Britpop reunion package tour with other bands, to which he said that “inevitably, it will happen”, but that “there&#39;s never really been a serious offer about &#39;The Big O&#39; getting back together, but there you go.”</p><p> In other news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-to-make-surprise-tram-announcements-in-manchester-this-week-3512560">it was revealed that Liam Gallagher would be this week&#39;s surprise voice for Manchester&#39;s tram announcements</a> .</p><p> The Manchester music legend is set to take over the tram announcements in celebration of the Bee Network, Greater Manchester&#39;s integrated public transport system, and Beyond the Music festival. Gallagher will be announcing the stops as they go via some pre-recorded snippets.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-promises-naughty-oasis-b-sides-on-definitely-maybe-tour-including-the-noel-sung-half-the-world-away-3513284">Liam Gallagher promises “naughty” Oasis B-sides on &#39;Definitely Maybe&#39; tour – including the Noel-sung &#39;Half The World Away&#39;</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
